      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i spend 10 hours a day staring at screens and the only person i've actually spoken to today was the delivery guy through a door. i feel like if i just stopped showing up to the calls or if i just... stopped being a presence online, it wouldn't even change anything. like i'm just a glitch in the system that everyone would just ignore.",
